productReviews.reviewText: My tyrannosaurus rex loves to play with it.
I tried to belly-flop it but got Turkish Delight all over it.
My neighbor Krista has one of these. She works as a salesman and she says it looks soapy.
I saw one of these in Saint Pierre and Miquelon and I bought one.
The box this comes in is 4 yard by 5 kilometer and weights 11 pound!
